# scrapers/ commits the CODE and each site's append-only archive.json (the
# dataset history — first_seen/last_seen cannot be reconstructed once lost).
# Everything else under data/ is generated or heavy and is owned by the running
# host + the live site, so it stays out of git.

# Generated build output (rebuilt from archive.json by build.py)
sites/*/data/data.json
# Latest upstream snapshot (regenerated every run)
sites/*/data/raw_latest.json
# Locally-downloaded product images (live on Hostinger; also under apps/autmog/images)
sites/*/data/images/
# Pre-fetch backup of archive.json
sites/*/data/archive.json.bak

# Python / OS noise
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.log
.DS_Store
